{"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Bye bye PerimeterX… Hello HumanSecurity","anchor":"Bye-bye-PerimeterX-Hello-HumanSecurity"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK name was changed from PerimeterX to HUMAN"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Android: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"import com.humansecurity.mobile_sdk.HumanSecurity"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"iOS: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"import HUMAN"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In Android you should change your "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"build.gradle"},{"type":"text","text":" file to you the new SDK repo location: https:\/\/jfrog.humansecurity.com\/artifactory\/human-android-sdk\/"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The main class was renamed from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PerimeterX"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HumanSecurity","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All SDK’s classes now have "},{"code":"HS","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" as a prefix to their name instead of ","type":"text"},{"code":"PX","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Some functions in ","type":"text"},{"code":"PerimeterX","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" were moved to ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSBotDefender","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSAccountDefender","type":"reference"},{"text":" classes according to their context.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PerimeterXDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" has been renamed to "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSBotDefenderDelegate"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Error query functions were combined into ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSBotDefender\/errorType(error:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" function.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Android’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"HSTimeoutInterceptor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" class was removed, you can set the different timeouts directly in the okHttp client config.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"The policy","anchor":"The-policy"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Previously the policy object was a one-level object that includes all SDK’s configurations.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Now the policy object includes the following objects:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSAutomaticInterceptorPolicy","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" - “Automatic Interceptor” configurations."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSHybridAppPolicy"},{"type":"text","text":" = “Hybrid App” configurations."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSDetectionPolicy","type":"reference"},{"text":" - Configurations regarding the SDK’s detection.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSDoctorAppPolicy","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" - “Doctor App” configurations."}]}]}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Previously you had to set your server(s) domain(s) for both the “Automatic Interceptor” and “Hybrid App”. Now, there are two different functions for each of them."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Bot-Defender","text":"Bot Defender","type":"heading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Previously the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSBotDefender\/headersForURLRequest(forAppId:)","isActive":true},{"text":" function returns ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"\/","type":"text"},{"code":"null","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" when you call it before calling the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HumanSecurity\/start(appId:policy:)"},{"type":"text","text":" function."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Now this function will always return a value (not empty). However, It’s mandatory to call it "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"after","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" calling the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HumanSecurity\/start(appId:policy:)"},{"text":" function.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Hybrid-App","text":"Hybrid App","type":"heading"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In order to enable “Hybrid App”, you should call the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSHybridAppPolicy\/set(webRootDomains:forAppId:)","type":"reference"},{"text":" function. Notice that you should set the ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"web root domain","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" (","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".example.com"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"New in iOS","anchor":"New-in-iOS"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HumanSecurity\/setupWebView(webView:navigationDelegate:)"},{"text":" function allows to do the “Hybrid App” integration manually, unlike the automatic way that was only available in previous versions.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSHybridAppPolicy\/automaticSetup"},{"text":" is an option to enable the same “Hybrid App” automatic integration that was available in previous versions.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Environment","anchor":"Environment"},{"text":"Android","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Android"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK is now built for API 34 and Kotlin 2.0.0."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The SDK has a new list of dependencies (see bellow). When fetching the SDK from our artifactory, those dependencies are automatically included. However, if you need to change the version of some dependencies, you may integrate the SDK manually and select the exact version that works for your app.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"groovy","code":["implementation 'androidx.core:core-ktx:1.13.1' \/\/ any version (select 1.10.1 if your app targets API 33)","implementation 'androidx.lifecycle:lifecycle-process:2.8.2' \/\/ min v2.6.0","implementation 'androidx.datastore:datastore-preferences:1.1.1' \/\/ any version (select 1.0.0 if your app targets API 33)","implementation 'com.google.android.material:material:1.12.0' \/\/ min v1.6.0","implementation 'com.fasterxml.uuid:java-uuid-generator:4.3.0' \/\/ min v3.0.0","implementation 'io.ktor:ktor-client-okhttp:2.3.11' \/\/ min v2.2.1"]}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"There are few major changes in the SDK’s API. In this article we will cover all of them."}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"HUMAN"}],"title":"How to upgrade from v3","role":"article"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/How_to_upgrade_from_v3"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN"]]},"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/human\/how_to_upgrade_from_v3"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/human\/how_to_upgrade_from_v3"]}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk/documentation/HUMAN/HSHybridAppPolicy/automaticSetup":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.perimeterx.mobile-sdk\/documentation\/HUMAN\/HSHybridAppPolicy\/automaticSetup","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"automaticSetup","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"automaticSetup","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/human\/hshybridapppolicy\/automaticsetup","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"When this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type